        "installation": "<p>Option 1:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to WordPress Dashboard-&gt;Plugins-&gt;Add New</li>\n<li>Search WooCommerce Coupons by Categories and Tags plugin using search option</li>\n<li>Find the plugin and click Install Now button</li>\n<li>After installation, click on Activate Plugin link to activate the plugin.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Option 2:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Download the plugin woocommerce-coupons-category-tag.zip</li>\n<li>Unpack the woocommerce-coupons-category-tag.zip file and extract the woocommerce-coupons-category-tag folder</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder to your /wp-content/plugins/ directory</li>\n<li>Go to WordPress dashboard, click on Plugins from the menu</li>\n<li>Locate the WooCommerce Coupons by Categories and Tags plugin and click on Activate link to activate the plugin.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Option 3:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Download the plugin woocommerce-coupons-category-tag.zip</li>\n<li>Go to WordPress Dashboard-&gt;Plugins-&gt;Add New</li>\n<li>Click on Upload Plugin link from top</li>\n<li>Upload the downloaded woocommerce-coupons-category-tag.zip file and click on Install Now</li>\n<li>After installation, click on Activate Plugin link to activate the plugin.</li>\n</ol>\n",
